   <concept id="FAR_22_1705"
            ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.2"
            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">22.1705</ph> Solicitation provision and contract clause.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d1473e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1495e10" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
               </p>
               <ol id="d1473e23" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1495e15" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                 Insert the clause at <xref href="52.222-50.dita#FAR_52_222_50"
                              base="i1056535"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.222-50</xref>, Combating Trafficking in Persons, in all solicitations and contracts.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1495e23" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                 Use the clause with its Alternate I when the contract will be performed outside the United States (as defined at <xref href="22.1702.dita#FAR_22_1702"
                              base="i1095538"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">22.1702</xref>) and the contracting officer has been notified of specific U.S. directives or notices regarding combating trafficking in persons (such as general orders or military listings of "off-limits" local establishments) that apply to contractor employees at the contract place of performance.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1495e31" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						             Insert the provision at <xref href="52.222-56.dita#FAR_52_222_56"
                        base="i1056889"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-56</xref>, Certification Regarding Trafficking in Persons Compliance Plan, in solicitations if</p>
               <ol id="d1473e62" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1495e40" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                 It is possible that at least 
									$550,000
								 of the value of the contract may be performed outside the United States; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1495e45" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                 The acquisition is not entirely for commercially available off-the-shelf items.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
